---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions | Ocala Golf Cart Rentals">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-600 to-emerald-800 text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
        Terms & Conditions
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-emerald-100">
        Please read these terms and conditions carefully before using our golf cart rental services.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Terms & Conditions Content -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
          <strong>Last updated:</strong> December 20, 2024
        </p>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-4">1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            By renting a golf cart from Ocala Golf Cart Rentals, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-4">2. Rental Requirements</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">To rent a golf cart, you must:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <li>Be at least 18 years of age</li>
            <li>Possess a valid driver's license</li>
            <li>Provide a valid credit card for security deposit</li>
            <li>Agree to our rental terms and conditions</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We reserve the right to refuse service to anyone at our discretion.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-4">3. Rental Periods and Pricing</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Rental periods and pricing are as follows:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <li><strong>Daily Rentals:</strong> 3-day minimum required, starting at $50/day</li>
            <li><strong>Weekly Rentals:</strong> Starting at $300/week</li>
            <li><strong>Monthly Rentals:</strong> Starting at $600/month</li>
            <li><strong>Fleet Rentals:</strong> Custom pricing based on quantity and duration</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            All pricing is subject to change without notice. Contact us for current rates and special event pricing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-4">4. Security Deposit</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            A security deposit is required for all rentals. The deposit amount varies based on the rental period and cart type. The deposit will be refunded upon return of the golf cart in satisfactory condition, minus any damages or additional charges.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-4">5. Golf Cart Operation</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">When operating our golf carts, you agree to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <li>Operate the golf cart safely and responsibly</li>
            <li>Follow all applicable traffic laws and regulations</li>
            <li>Not exceed the maximum passenger capacity</li>
            <li>Not operate under the influence of alcohol or drugs</li>
            <li>Not use the golf cart for racing or reckless driving</li>
            <li>Not modify or alter the golf cart in any way</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-4">6. Damage and Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            You are responsible for any damage to the golf cart during your rental period. This includes damage from accidents, misuse, or negligence. We recommend operating the golf cart safely and within designated areas.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Ocala Golf Cart Rentals is not liable for personal injury or property damage that may occur while using our golf carts. Renters assume all risk associated with golf cart operation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-4">7. Cancellation Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Cancellations must be made at least 24 hours in advance of the scheduled rental start time. Cancellations made within 24 hours may be subject to a cancellation fee.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-4">8. Delivery and Pickup</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            We provide free delivery and pickup within Ocala city limits. Extended delivery areas may incur additional charges. Delivery and pickup times will be coordinated based on availability and your schedule.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-4">9. Fuel and Maintenance</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            All golf carts are delivered with a full tank of gas. Renters are responsible for refueling the golf cart before return. Golf carts must be returned in the same condition as received, normal wear and tear excepted.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-4">10. Weather and Force Majeure</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            We are not responsible for delays or cancellations due to weather conditions, natural disasters, or other circumstances beyond our control. In such cases, we will work with you to reschedule or provide appropriate accommodations.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-4">11. Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Your privacy is important to us. Please review our Privacy Policy to understand how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-4">12. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            We reserve the right to modify these Terms and Conditions at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting on our website. Continued use of our services after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-4">13. Contact Information</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            If you have any questions about these Terms and Conditions, please contact us:
          </p>
          <div class="bg-emerald-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>Ocala Golf Cart Rentals</strong></p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">Phone: <a href="tel:+13527801526" class="text-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-700">(352) 780-1526</a></p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">Email: <a href="mailto:golfcartrentalocala@gmail.com" class="text-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-700">golfcartrentalocala@gmail.com</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
